# 0.3.0

🆕 features

- Add theme support
- Add caching to further reduce load times
- Add 404 error page
- Add thumbnail generation
- Introduce cache control flag
- Get rid of /static/ on dev time (will be compiled in the Dockerfile)
- Add https://github.com/edwardtufte/tufte-css based theme "plain"

# 0.2.0

🐛 bug fixes

- Fixed an issue causing the feed to not display the post content as HTML

🆕 features

- Add file upload/ delete
- Add insert of images into posts
- Added post tags
- Add image post preview
- Removed meta[name='generator'] tag
- Add image resizing on upload


# 0.1.0

- Added Dockerfile for initial deployment